How to use this package:

This is a basic structure based on CC's code standards, defined by Front-end team. You must use this structure if you want to improve the usage of standard definitions of this company. If you don't want to use this - you're a free person - you must follow the code standards and probably you would have to build a similar structure.

Feel free to remove all unused folders and files.

Before go live, please, don't forget to:

* remove the vendor folder on live version (if it isn't being used).
* minify javascript and css files
* .htaccess - remove concatenate rules or use the example that comes on basic structure.
* validate your HTML and CSS.
* verify SEO checklist.
* write on confluence page some basic information about how to deploy the app. Explain in a single step by step list to avoid mistakes in the future.